quran[33]{c,v,t}:
  18,99,"Uye pazuva iroro (pachabuda vana Gog naMagog), tichasiya vamwe vavo vachiita kunge masaisai pane vamwe vavo, uye hwamanda icharidzwa, uye tichavaunganidza pamwe chete"
  18,100,Uye pazuva iroro ticharatidza Gehena kune avo vasingatendi zviri pachena
  18,101,"Avo maziso avo akanga akavharwa kurangaridzo yangu, uye vakanga vasingakwanisi kunzwa (chokwadi)"
  18,102,"Avo vasingatendi vanofunga here kuti vangatore varanda vangu (ngirozi, vatumwa) sevabetseri kunze kwangu? Zvirokwazvo, takagadzira Gehena semafaro evasingatendi (muhumwechete hwaAllah)"
  18,103,"Iti (Muhammad (SAW)): “Tikuudzei here vakarasikirwa zvikuru mumabasa?”"
  18,104,"“Avo mabasa avo akatambisika muhupenyu hwepano pasi, asi vachifunga kuti varikuwana zvakanaka nemabasa avo.”"
  18,105,"“Ndeavo vanoramba zviratidzo zvaTenzi vavo uye nekusangana navo (muzuva rekumutswa). Naizvozvo mabasa avo achashaya basa, uye muzuva rekumutswa hatimbovapi huremu.”"
  18,106,"“Uyo mubairo wavo, iGehena, nekuti vairamba kutenda, uye vaitora zviratidzo zvangu nevatumwa vangu sedambe.”"
  18,107,"“Zvirokwazvo avo vanotenda (muIslaam) uye voita mabasa akanaka, vachawana minda ye Al- Firdaus (Paradhiso) yemafaro"
  18,108,Vachagara imomo zvachose. Havamboshuviri kubuda imomo
  18,109,"Iti (Muhammad (SAW) kune vanhu): “Dai gungwa raiva ingi yekunyora mazwi aTenzi vangu, zvirokwazvo, gungwa ringadai rakapwa mazwi aTenzi vangu asati apera, kunyangwe tikaunza (rimwe gungwa) rakafanana kunowedzera.”"
  18,110,"Iti (Muhammad (SAW)): “Zvirokwazvo, ndiri munhu semi. Zvakadzikiswa kwandiri kuti Mwari wenyu ndiMwari mumwechete. Naizvozvo uyo anoshuvira kusangana naTenzi vake, ngaaite mabasa akanaka, uye ngaasasanganise umwe mukunamata Tenzi vake.”"
  19,1,"Kaaf – Haa – Yaa – Ain – Swaad. (Aya mashoko ndemamwe ezvishamiso zviri muQur’aan, uye hakuna kana ani zvake anoziva zvaanoreva kunze kwaAllah)"
  19,2,(Iyi ndiyo) bufuro (ziviso) yetsitsi dzaTenzi vako kune muranda wavo Zakariyya (Zakero)
  19,3,Apo paakadaidzira kuna Tenzi vake (Allah) daidziro yakavanda
  19,4,"Akataura achiti: “Tenzi vangu (Allah)! Zvirokwazvo, mapfupa angu ava anoregwedeka (apera simba), uye pfupfu yave inopararira musoro (imvi dzapararira musoro), uye handina kumbobvira ndaomera kukukumbirai (muminamato yangu), Tenzi vangu (Allah)!”"
  19,5,"“Uye zvirokwazvo, ndinotya hama dzangu mushure mangu, uye mukadzi wangu ingomwa (haana mbereko). Naizvozvo (ndinokumbirawo) mundipewo mugari wenhaka (yangu) kubva kwamuri.”"
  19,6,"“(Uyo) achandigara nhaka, uye achazogara nhaka (Ruzivo nehuporofita kwete mari) kubva mumhuri yaYa’qoob (Jakobho). Uye ivai munoita kuti (mwana uyu wandiri kukukumbirai) ave anokufadzai, (imi) Tenzi vangu!”"
  19,7,"(Allah vakati): “Iwe Zakariyya (Zakero)! Zvirokwazvo, tirikukupa mashoko anofadza emwanakomana, zita rake ndiYahya (Johwani). Hatisati tambopa zita iri kunani-nani zvake kubvira makare.”"
  19,8,"(Zakero) akati: “Tenzi vangu! Zvirokwazvo, ndingaite mwanakomana seiko apo mudzimai wangu ingomwa (haana mbereko), uye ndave mukweguri (akurisa)?”"
  19,9,"(Allah) ndokuti: “Nokudaro (zvichaitika). Tenzi vako (Allah) vanoti: Zvirinyore kwandiri. Uye (iwe Zakero) ndakave ndinokusika mushure apo pawakanga usiri chinhu!”"
  19,10,"Zakariyya (Zakero) akave anoti: “Tenzi vangu! Nditaridzeiwo chiratidzo.” Ndokubva (Allah) vati: “Chiratidzo chako ndechekuti uchave unoregedza kutaura nevanhu kwehusiku hutatu, nyangwe hazvo pasina chinokanganisa muviri.”"
  19,11,Pedzezvo (Zakariyya) akabuda munzvimbo yokunamatira (Al-Mihraab) akava anovaudza (kuburikidza) nezviratidzo kuti vave vanorumbidza Allah mangwanani pamwe nemasikati
  19,12,"(Zvakanzi kumwana wake): “Iwe Yahya (Johwani)! Iva unobatisisa (unotora) Gwaro (Torah) zvine simba (zvakasimba).” Uye takava tinomupa njere dzakarurama achiri mwana"
  19,13,"Uye takava tinomuita kuti ave munhu anerudo nevamwe (anonzwisisa) setsitsi kubva kwatiri, uye takava tinomuchenura kubva muzvivi (iye Johwani), uye aive munhu akarurama (anotya Allah)"
  19,14,"Uye akanga ari munhu anopa vabereki vake kodzero dzavo, zvekare akanga asiri munhu anozvitutumadza pamwe nekusateerera (ivo Allah nevabereki vake)"
  19,15,"Uye runyararo ngaruve kwaari (kubva) zuva raakaberekwa, uye zuva iro raachashaya, pamwe nezuva iro raachamutswa kubva kuvafi"
  19,16,"Uye taura (Muhammad (SAW)) zviri muBhuku (Qur’aan maererano nenyaya ya) Maryam (Mariya), apo paakaenda ari oga achisiya mhuri yake kunzvimbo yakatarisana nekumabvazuva"
  19,17,"Naizvozvo akazvivharidzira kubva kwavari (kuti asaonekwa), ndokubva tamutumira Rooh yedu (Ngirozi Jibreel (Gabriel)) kwaari (Mariya), naizvozvo (Ngirozi Gabriel) yakatora mufananidzo wemunhu chaiye sezvaari"
  19,18,"(Mariya) akati: “Zvirokwazvo, ndinokumbira kudzivirirwa neane ngoni (naAllah) kubva kwauri, ndokunge kana uchitya Allah.”"
  19,19,"(Ngirozi) yakati: “Zvirokwazvo, ndiri mutumwa waTenzi vako, (ndirikuda kukuudza nezvefundaidzo) ndichifundaidza chipo pauri chemwanakomana akarurama.”"
  19,20,"(Maryam) ndokuti: “Ndingagoita mwanakomana seiko, apo hapana kana munhurume akambondibata, uye handisi pfambi?”"
  19,21,"(Ngirozi) yakati: “Nokudaro (zvichaitika). Tenzi vako vati: ‘Zvirinyore kwandiri (ini Allah). Uye tichamuita kuti ave chiratidzo kuvanhu uye setsitsi kubva kwatiri (Allah) zvekare, uye chiitiko chine chisungo kubva kuna Allah.’”"